{"tid":1132091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慎入！男頭部遭寄生蟲啃食　腦子有洞頭骨外露","createTime":"2019-04-30T05:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T07:09:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b19b70f7b4fab65ce9a4d376ef9bd36285fd2084","tid":1132091,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190427/640_f029d46d7aca1cf2ba10b2a069f78029.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190427%2F640_f029d46d7aca1cf2ba10b2a069f78029.jpg&h=f473ef38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞一名男子席爾瓦(Jhonatan de Jesus Castro Silva)，是一名遊民，不過有不少人發現他的腦子已經出現大洞，而且深可見骨，部分頭骨已露出。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，席爾瓦的父母在2年前過世，他曾經有嗑藥上癮的問題，並成為遊民流浪街頭。不過最近他被發現感染了「蠅蛆病」(myiasis)，被寄生蟲寄生在體內，而席爾瓦被寄生的部位剛好在頭部，不少人看見他的左後方頭部已經出現大洞，腦部被腐蝕，甚至頭骨外露，相當駭人。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方卡德納斯(Javier Cardenas)表示，其實當局曾經協助過席爾瓦，把他帶到救助中心3次，並為他清除了4000隻寄生蟲，但席爾瓦總是不願接受完整治療，從診療所偷跑出來，回到街頭繼續當遊民。席爾瓦的阿姨也說，看到席爾瓦「好像死屍走在街頭」，她也請大家救救他的外甥，不要讓他死在街頭。當地記者戴茲(Javier Diaz)表示，當地人暱稱席爾瓦為「喪屍」，但當記者們想要採訪他的時候，他會變得非常緊張且具攻擊性。<br />\n<br />\n報導也指出，後來席爾瓦被強制送醫治療，但住院的第一天晚上就從醫院跑出來，之後被找到，再被送進醫院，目前未知席爾瓦的治療進度如何。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190427/640_f71cef15891ed00ecbd05225c8af8a12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190427%2F640_f71cef15891ed00ecbd05225c8af8a12.jpg&h=58eaddd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a87cb8c504ab423ed46300d57cbcab56a830a6f","tid":1132091,"uid":193969,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"屌你呢啲又有圖"},{"pid":"879d1ce465b768aefc413609505892736b440b01","tid":1132091,"uid":28195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"右下 EA logo？？"},{"pid":"533540295fb3e46afd6e21d2d399fbc33166b09d","tid":1132091,"uid":191394,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:27:05.000Z","msg":"頂你 有格個張係下面<br />\n無格個張係上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccd24dd3187aee67be221d7fa0da54c66d95ff5","tid":1132091,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"喪屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb22e6ee800bead7361dc527aff8dd5a6cec5526","tid":1132091,"uid":215225,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McVJ2N0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcVJ2N0.png&h=7563ea96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPi32N3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPi32N3.png&h=4663d6ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThey sucked his brains out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f8611df674886246f0db773a2e1d5cdc2dbeee","tid":1132091,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"咁都唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dee1afde26b693b2a5c4db376e055e08f2c87b4","tid":1132091,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:26:44.000Z","msg":"咬撚到咁，好撚忍得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a21b487c843baa129bc4678af8ef5cf790f9ee6","tid":1132091,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:32:08.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無格係上面，有格係下面"},{"pid":"01ad29ebe7c59542b823a0573e620626e09d85d5","tid":1132091,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"我就知道一定有圖先入黎睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e4533649964e7570c6ce1656b4c61bcfe594c8","tid":1132091,"uid":109329,"